هل حصنت طفلك من التهاب السحايا؟
التهاب السحايا مرض معدي خطير يزيد التواجد بالأماكن المزدحمة كالمدارس من خطر إصابة الأطفال به، وتكمّن خطورته في سرعة تطوره التي قد تسبب الوفاة خلال 24 _ 48 ساعة! لذا تأكد من تحصين طفلك بحصوله على تطعيم التهاب السحايا وفقاً لجدول تطعيماته وكل 2 _ 3 أعوام لحمايته..
التطعيم متوفر بشكل دائم في مركز الحياة الطبي.

Did you protect your child from Meningits?
 Meningitis is a life-threatening infectious disease because its symptoms can quickly get worse and cause death within 24-48 hours. Being in crowded places, such as schools, increases the risk of children developing it, hence we advice you to immunize your child by getting a meningitis vaccination according to his vaccination schedule and every 2-3 years to protect him.
The vaccination is available at Al Hayat Medical Center.

ما هو لقاح سرطان عنق الرحم؟
لقاح سيرفاريكس هو لقاح متوفر في مركز الحياة الطبي يساعد على منع سرطان الرحم والحالات ما قبل السرطانية الناجمة عن العدوى بفيروس الورم الحليمي البشري نوع 16 و18، يُعطى اللقاح للإناث اللاتي تتراوح أعمارهن بين 10 – 55 عاماً ليساعد في الحماية من سرطان عنق الرحم عن طريق منع العدوى.
لمزيد من المعلومات يرجى زيارتنا على الرابط التالي:
https://cutt.us/eOkKT

What is cervical cancer vaccine?
Cervarix vaccine is a vaccine available at Al Hayat Medical Center that helps prevent infection by certain types of human papillomavirus such as  uterine cancer and pre-cancerous conditions.Available vaccines protect against either two, four, or nine types of HPV. All vaccines protect against at least HPV types 16 and 18, which cause the greatest risk of cervical cancer.
For more information, please visit us at the following link:
https://cutt.us/NAaQC

يساهم الكشف المبكر في علاج 80% من سرطانات عنق الرحم بحسب منظمة الصحة العالمية، ومسحة عنق الرحم فحص بسيط يتيح الكشف المبكر عن سرطان عنق الرحم بأخذ مسحة صغيرة من خلايا سطح عنق الرحم وفحصها مجهرياً للبحث عن أي تغير فيها.
ننصحكِ بالقيام باختبار عنق الرحم مباشرة بعد الزواج وتكراره كل 3 سنوات وهو متوفر في مركز الحياة الطبي. 
What is a Pap smear?
Early detection helpsin curing 80% of cervical cancers, according to the World Health Organization. A Pap smear is a simple examination that  detects cervical cancer early by taking a small smear from the cells of the cervical surface and examining it microscopically to look for any changes in it.
We recommend that you do a Pap smear test immediately after marriage and repeat it every 3 years, it is available at Al Hayat Medical Center.

يُعدّ سرطان عنق الرحم رابع أكثر السرطانات شيوعاً بحسب منظمة الصحة العالمية، ينشأ المرض تدريجياً عند النساء نتيجة وجود نمو غير طبيعي لخلايا عنق الرحم (الجزء السفلي من الرحم المتصل بالمهبل).
تستطيعين تقليل خطر سرطان عنق الرحم عن طريق القيام بمسحة عنق الرحم دورياً للكشف المبكر، وتلقي لقاح سرطان عنق الرحم للفتيات والسيدات.

Cervical cancer is the fourth most common cancer, according to the World Health Organization (WHO). The disease gradually develop in women as a result of the abnormal growth of cervical cells ( the lower part of the uterus thatu is connected to the vagina).
You can reduce the risk of cervical cancer by periodically performing a Pap 
smear for early detection, and by receiving cervical cancer vaccine.

You can also enjoy both in one session for unresistable results 😉

Did you know that most cases of sleep disturbances and stress are caused by tinnitus?
The tinnitus is a condition in which the patient hears a ringing or annoying sound in the ear, which may be the result of aging, ear blockage, injury, or a problem with the circulatory system or other problems, if you get tinnitus without any apparent reason especially if it is accompanied by dizziness or hearing loss please visit the doctor.

فالكثير من السيدات معرضات للإصابة بأمراض اللثة أثناء الحمل بسبب التغيرات الهرمونية التي تصيبهن خلال هذه الفترة، حيث تلعب الزيادة في نسب بعض الهرمونات دوراً في نمو البكتيريا وجعل أنسجة اللثة أكثر استجابة للسموم.

Have you thought about visiting a dentist during your pregnancy?
Hormonal changes during pregnancy can make your gums more vulnerable to plaque, leading to inflammation and bleeding. This is also called pregnancy gingivitis or gum disease.
Where the increase in the ratios of some hormones plays a role in the growth of bacteria and making gum tissue more responsive to toxins.

Cold or flu?
Cold and flu are two different illnesses, despite their similar symptoms. Cold symptoms begin gradually, while the flu suddenly appears with muscle pain, and sometimes serious complications that can not be ignored, so we always care at Al Hayat Medical Center to provide seasonal flu vaccine for all ages.

What are Dry Eyes?
A stinging, burning or scratchy sensation in your eyes with heaviness in the eyelids and redness of the eye, symptoms that may indicate "Dry Eyes",Dry eyes may occur if you don't produce enough tears or if you produce poor-quality tears.
the condition usually requires simple treatment, but it may develop and cause complications if not treated correctly under Eye specialist supervision.

Does gestational diabetes increase risk of diabetes in child?
A woman with gestational diabetes is at higher risk of having it another time in a second pregnancy or having a second type of diabetes later in life, so she shouldregularly check her blood sugar even after giving birth, but there is no relationshipbetween gestational diabetes and babies having diabetes.
